  <source>Stanford University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to better understand the underlying pathogenetic mechanisms of
      MPDs. We will collect peripheral blood samples from MPD patients and utilize multiparameter
      phospho-specific flow cytometry to investigate dysregulated signaling in blood cells from
      these patients. This will provide deeper insights into the pathogenesis of MPDs and may lead
      to the identification of novel targets for therapeutic intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
